{"tid":368510,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《神奇女俠》狂收31億票房成今年暑期票房之冠","createTime":"2017-08-21T15:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T06:24:32.000Z","uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14c69aa62fcf7114ebe6283a248d468563c8e720","tid":368510,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"暑期即將完結，亦係時候作票房大結算！6月上映的DC超級英雄大片《神奇女俠》（Wonder Woman）累積收入高達31.3億港元而成為今年北美暑期票房之冠。僅次於《神》就是DC對家漫威（Marvel）的超英大片《銀河守護隊2》（Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2），該片勁收30.3億港元。至於第3位亦是漫威的超英大片《蜘蛛俠：強勢回歸》（Spider-Man： Homecoming），影片狂收24億港元。光映娛樂（Illumination Entertainment）的省招牌動畫系列《壞蛋掌門人3》（Despicable Me 3）以19億港元排第4位，成為今年暑期最賣座動畫。其餘打入十大就是《加勒比海盜：惡靈啟航》（Pirates of the Caribbean：Dead Men Tell No Tales）、《鄧寇克大行動》（Dunkirk）、《反斗車王3》（Cars 3）、《猿人爭霸戰：猩凶巨戰》（War for the Planet of the Apes）、《變形金剛：終極戰士》（Transformers: The Last Knight）及《寶貝神車手》（Baby Driver）。<br />\n另方面，《寶》美國新星安索艾果特（Ansel Elgort）近日就同女友Violetta Komyshan飛抵北京宣傳新片，期間二人遊覽長城與天安門廣場之外亦一同打邊爐！"},{"pid":"03495f5b8f7cd60d3443b17fa8674487821a577c","tid":368510,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:03:05.000Z","msg":"戰狼2 50億啦"},{"pid":"597b58b03b83c5b6b8fd3fa9a3cb84a006083984","tid":368510,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰狼2 50億啦</blockquote><br />\n作夠100億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2978ca735cf3ebce67124d0a1ae122d4f66b1c43","tid":368510,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"DC Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3956ebcb4c1b5f3390b39ef511c9061b7077ed","tid":368510,"uid":38555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"竟然冇ff8"},{"pid":"8381f09b0a007b5e31301946f6c40df25d17837d","tid":368510,"uid":16031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:20: